object.script: -- Author: Toastery -- GitHub: https://github.com/Toast732 -- Workshop: -- -- Developed & Minimized using LifeBoatAPI - Stormworks Lua plugin for VSCode -- https://code.visualstudio.com/download (search "Stormworks Lua with LifeboatAPI" extension) -- By Nameous Changey -- Minimized Size: 3110 (3424) chars bM="normal_road_speed" bL="normal_offroad_speed" bK="aggressive_road_speed" bJ="aggressive_bridge_speed" bI="normal_bridge_speed" bH="aggressive_offroad_speed" bG=178 bF=57.2 bE=.1 bD=true bC=false bB=input bA=output bz=math by=bz.abs bx=bA.setBool bw=bz.max bv=bB.getNumber bu=bA.setNumber bt=bz.random bs=property.getNumber local b=0 local c=bC local d=bs("random_speed_range")local e={[0]={[0]=0,[1]=0},[1]={[0]=bt(bs(bM)-d,bs(bM)+d),[1]=bt(bs(bK)-d,bs(bK)+d)},[2]={[0]=bt(bs(bL)-d,bs(bL)+d),[1]=bt(bs(bH)-d,bs(bH)+d)},[3]={[0]=bt(bs(bI)-d,bs(bI)+d),[1]=bt(bs(bJ)-d,bs(bJ)+d)}}function f(g,h)return bt()*(h-g)+g end function i(j,k,l,m)return bz.deg(bz.atan(l-j,m-k))end function n(l,m,j,k)return bz.sqrt((j-l)^2+(k-m)^2)end function o(p,q)if p>q then return bD else return bC end end function r(s,t,u,v)if not t then bu(1,s)else local w=bs("aggressive_behaviour")local x=1 if w==0 then x=bv(13)elseif w==1 then x=0 end local y=1 if v<100 and x==0 then y=v/100 elseif v<50 then y=v/50 end local z=bv(14)if s>0 then local A=bs("minimum_speed_random_range")local B=bs("minimum_speed")+f(-A,-A)if x==1 then B=B*1.5 end bu(1,bw(e[z][x]/bw(u/90,1)*(y),B))else bu(1,0)end end end local C=bs("turning_rate_random_range")local D=bs("turning_rate")+f(-C,-C)function E(s,F)if not F then bu(2,s)else local G=b-bw(bz.min(b-s,D),-D)bu(2,G)b=G end end function onTick()local H=bs("steering_type")local I=bs("front_dist_tolerance")local J=bs("front_down_dist_tolerance")local K=bs("rear_dist_tolerance")local L=bs("rear_down_dist_tolerance")local M=bs("wall_safe_dist")local N=bs("ground_safe_dist")local O=bs("tank_turn_speed")local P=bB.getBool(1)local Q=bv(1)local R=bv(2)local S=bv(3)local T=bv(4)local U=bv(15)local V=bv(16)local W=bv(5)*-360 local X=i(Q,R,S,T)local Y=bv(6)local Z=bv(7)local bb=bv(8)local bc=bv(9)local bd=bv(10)local be=bv(11)local bf=Y-I local bg=Z-J local bh=bb-J local bi=bc-K local bj=bd-L local bk=be-L if S~=0 or T~=0 then v=n(Q,R,S,T)bl=n(Q,R,U,V)bu(5,v)if bl>2 and P then bx(1,bD)bu(3,W)local bm=X-W bu(5,X)bu(6,bm)if H==0 then local bn=bs("steering_max_angle")local bo=bv(12)if bm>91 or bm<-91 then if not c then bx(2,bD)r(0)E(0,bD)bx(3,bD)if bo<bE then c=bD bx(3,bC)end else bx(3,bC)E(-(bm/90*bn/bF),bD)r(1,bD,bm,bl)bx(2,bD)c=bD end bu(7,1)elseif o(bf,M)then if c then bx(2,bC)r(0,bD,bm,bl)E(0,bD)bx(3,bD)if bo<bE then c=bC bx(3,bC)end else bx(3,bC)E((bm/90*bn/bF),bD)r(1,bD,bm,bl)bx(2,bC)c=bC end bu(7,2)elseif o(bi,M)then if not c then bx(2,bD)r(0)E(0,bD)bx(3,bD)if bo<bE then c=bD bx(3,bC)end else bx(3,bC)E(-(bm/90*bn/bF),bD)r(1,bD,bm,bl)bx(2,bD)c=bD end bu(7,3)else bx(2,bC)bx(1,bC)r(0)E(0,bD)bu(7,4)end elseif H==1 then local bp=1 if v<50 then bp=bw(v/50,.7)end local bq=1 if by(bm)<50 then bq=bw(by(bm)/50,.4)end bu(4,bq)if bm<2 and bm>-2 then if o(bf,M)then r(1*bp)E(0)end elseif bm>bG and br<182 or bm<-bG and bm>-182 then if o(bf,M)then r(-1*bp)E(0)end elseif bm<-2 and bm>=-bG then if o(N,bg)and o(N,bk)then E(-O*bq)if bq==1 then r(0)else r((.08/bq))end end else if o(N,bh)and o(N,bj)then E(O*bq)if bq==1 then r(0)else r((.08/bq))end end end end else bu(7,5)bx(1,bC)end end end
